endpoints.description:
Upserts a new scenario for a sandbox, keying off of the optionally provided scenario id.

If an id is provided and has a match, the scenario will be updated. If no id is provided or no match
is found, a new scenario will be appended to the end.

Note that a full replacement of the scenario is performed, so any fields not provided will be removed
or overwritten with default values.
endpoints.name: Upsert Sandbox Scenario

pathParameters.description: A UUID string identifying this sandbox.

properties.description: The inputs for the scenario
The id of the scenario to update. If none is provided, an id will be generated and a new scenario will be appended.

endpoints.description: Deletes an existing scenario from a sandbox, keying off of the provided scenario id.
endpoints.name: Delete Sandbox Scenario

pathParameters.description: A UUID string identifying this sandbox.
An id identifying the scenario that you'd like to delete

endpoints.description:
Upserts a new test case for a test suite, keying off of the optionally provided test case id.

If an id is provided and has a match, the test case will be updated. If no id is provided or no match
is found, a new test case will be appended to the end.

Note that a full replacement of the test case is performed, so any fields not provided will be removed
or overwritten with default values.
endpoints.name: Upsert Test Suite Test Case

pathParameters.description: A UUID string identifying this test suite.

properties.description: The id of the test case to update. If none is provided, an id will be generated and a new test case will be appended.
A human-friendly label for the test case.
Key/value pairs for each input variable that the Test Suite expects.
Parameters to use when evaluating the test case, specific to the test suite's evaluation metric.
